<p>The code you posted lists <code>"Camera"</code> as the name of the camera in the <code>PhotonCamera</code> constructor. You may need to update this to align with the setup in the UI website for photonvision.</p>
<aside class="quote no-group" data-username="Konnor" data-post="9" data-topic="407685">
<div class="title">
