<blockquote>
<p>So i should change the camera name to Yellow or Blue alliance accordingly? Or should i just set the pipeline?</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>The requirement is the name provided in the UI and the name set in code must match. This is required because you might have multiple cameras, or multiple coprocessors, all running photonvision. You must make your code align to the camera you want to use vision results from.</p>
